i want to make it so when u right click with sword it cobwebs but its sending to many packets when using with a shield because it spams anytime u right click not just when a cobweb is placeable - def module web-trap-slow
def desc "Places a web with a fixed 0.05s delay and 1s cooldown after use"

on right_click if playing if holding #sword {
   switch :cobweb
   wait 0.05
   input use
   wait 0.05
   switch #sword
   wait 1.0
}